        <div class="chapter" id="figures">
            <div class="chapter-header">
                <h2>10. Original Figures</h2>
            </div>
            <p>下面保留了本次写作中最关键的原图，方便快速对照论文结构回看。</p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                <figure class="card overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="/notes/on-policy-distillation/opd-teaser.png" alt="OPD teaser" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/70" />
                    <figcaption class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">图 1：OPD 全文总览</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="card overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="/notes/on-policy-distillation/3-1-metrics.png" alt="Phenomenology metrics" class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/70" />
                    <figcaption class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">图 2：成功条件与现象对比</figcaption>
